title: The Drums - Post Punk Idol Rock (formerly Elkland)
description:
Post-punk idol rock from The Drums, featuring the vocalist from (and similar sound to) synthpop group Elkland (aka Goat Explosion).

6 tracks from their upcoming album:

1. The Drums - Best Friend
2. The Drums - Down by the Water
3. The Drums - I'll Never Drop My Sword
4. The Drums - Let's Go Surfing
5. The Drums - Me and the Moon
6. The Drums - Submarine
